snippet.title: Quetzal's Call | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Quetzal's Call is now available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1953670/Quetzals_Call/ 

Experience the rush of soaring, dashing, and leaping with unmatched agility as you navigate intricate levels and test your skills in a vibrant, treacherous world.

Music by tissue inu.
Follow us on X: https://x.com/tissueinu 
Follow us on Bluesky: https://bsky.app/profile/tissueinu.bsky.social 

#indiegame #platformer #gamedev
